== 參數及使用方法 ==
This template formats IPA transcriptions and links them to [[Help:奧克語國際音標]]. The transcription should match the conventions of that key; for narrower dialect transcriptions, use {{tl|IPA-all}}, which links to a more complete IPA key. 

The first cell in the template is for the transcription, and a second optional cell is a switch that controls the lede. With no second value, the lede ''Occitan pronunciation:'' appears: 
*<code><nowiki>{{IPA-oc|tu}}</nowiki></code> → {{IPA-oc|tu}}
*<code><nowiki>{{IPA-oc|tu|pron}}</nowiki></code> → {{IPA-oc|tu|pron}}
*<code><nowiki>{{IPA-oc|tu|lang}}</nowiki></code> → {{IPA-oc|tu|lang}}
*<code><nowiki>{{IPA-oc|tu|IPA}}</nowiki></code> → {{IPA-oc|tu|IPA}}
*<code><nowiki>{{IPA-oc|tu|}}</nowiki></code> → {{IPA-oc|tu|}}

Any of these may be combined with a sound file in an optional third cell:
*<code><nowiki>{{IPA-oc|tu|IPA|Es-tú.ogg}}</nowiki></code> → {{IPA-oc|tu|IPA|Es-tú.ogg}}

For the default lede, however, a placeholder such as ‹-› is required in the second cell: 
*<code><nowiki>{{IPA-oc|tu|-|Es-tú.ogg}}</nowiki></code> → {{IPA-oc|tu|-|Es-tú.ogg}}

